Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:17.17,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Sì, pare che sarà un\N bel festival sportivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:18.89,Fuoricampo,,0,0,0,,Lo sarà certamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:26.25,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Beh, meno male.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:27.14,Dialogo,,0,0,0,,Andiamo.
